Analyzing usage patterns and trends to enhance our services and user 
experience.
Protecting our rights, preventing fraud, and ensuring the security of our 
services.
Complying with legal obligations and resolving any disputes.
Information Sharing and Disclosure
We may share your personal information with third parties in the following 
circumstances:
